Dahlberg Inc said it completed apreviously announced agreement with Sears, Roebuck and Co tooperate hearing aid centers in sears stores on a nationalbasis.    Dahlberg currently operates some 142 hearing aid centers ona concession basis in Sears stores.    In connection with the program, the company said it grantedSears an option to buy up to 300,000 shares of Dahlberg stockat 12 dlrs a share. Reuter&#3;